// 개인 Notion의 자동화 부서 가이드와 오픈AI 인증 자료를 Pages·Prompts에 저장한다
import { randomUUID } from "crypto";
import { existsSync, readFileSync } from "fs";
import { dirname, resolve } from "path";
import { fileURLToPath } from "url";
import { createClient } from "@supabase/supabase-js";
import Database from "better-sqlite3";

const root = resolve(dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)), "..");
const envPath = resolve(root, ".env.local");
if (existsSync(envPath)) {
  for (const line of readFileSync(envPath, "utf8").split("\n")) {
    const match = line.match(/^([^#=]+)=(.*)$/);
    if (!match || process.env[match[1].trim()]) continue;
    process.env[match[1].trim()] = match[2]
      .trim()
      .replace(/^(["'])|(["'])$/g, "");
  }
}

const { markdownToTiptapDoc } = await import(
  resolve(root, "src/lib/markdown-to-tiptap.ts")
);

const PROD_USER = "f72e9a44-79d8-4061-a700-3ec50bb04a97";
const LOCAL_USER = "dev";
const CATEGORY = "Claude Skills · 7개 자동화 부서";
const now = new Date().toISOString();

const pageDefinitions = [
  {
    key: "departments",
    title: "🏢 7개 자동화 부서",
    source:
      "https://app.notion.com/p/gilwon/7-85bb256827ac8370bc1f815de190b766?source=copy_link",
    raw: Buffer.from("", "base64").toString("utf8"),
  },
  {
    key: "openai-certification",
    title: "🎓 오픈AI 공식 AI 인증 — 컴활 자리를 대체할 '증명서'",
    source:
      "https://app.notion.com/p/gilwon/AI-AI-52bb256827ac82aa9e8f81ae45a72e66?source=copy_link",
    raw: Buffer.from("", "base64").toString("utf8"),
  },
];

function normalizeNotionMarkdown(page) {
  const content = page.raw
    .replace(/<callout[^>]*>\n?/g, "")
    .replace(/\n?<\/callout>/g, "")
    .replace(/<br\s*\/?>/g, "\n")
    .replace(/^\t/gm, "")
    .replace(/\\~/g, "~")
    .replace(/\n{4,}/g, "\n\n\n")
    .trim();

  return `> 원문. [Notion](${page.source})\n\n${content}\n`;
}

function cleanPromptText(value) {
  return value
    .replace(/\*\*/g, "")
    .replace(/`/g, "")
    .replace(/\[([^\]]+)\]\([^)]+\)/g, "$1")
    .replace(/\s+/g, " ")
    .replace(/\s*[→.]\s*클로드.*$/, "")
    .trim()
    .replace(/\.$/, "");
}

const departmentPage = pageDefinitions[0];
const skillCallouts = [
  ...departmentPage.raw.matchAll(/<callout[^>]*>\n([\s\S]*?)\n<\/callout>/g),
].map((match) => match[1]);
const prompts = skillCallouts
  .map((callout) => {
    const name = callout.match(/\*\*([^*]+)\*\*\s*—/)?.[1];
    const usage = callout.match(
      /·\s*(?:\*\*)?(?:쓰기|사용 방법)(?:\*\*)?:\s*([\s\S]*)/
    )?.[1];
    if (!name || !usage || name === "verification") return null;

    const example = usage.match(/예:\s*(?:"([^"]+)"|`([^`]+)`)/);
    const direct = usage.match(/(?:"([^"]+)"|`([^`]+)`)/);
    const body = cleanPromptText(
      example?.[1] ?? example?.[2] ?? direct?.[1] ?? direct?.[2] ?? ""
    );
    if (!body) return null;

    const description = callout.match(
      /·\s*(?:\*\*)?(?:좋은 점|무엇을 해주나)(?:\*\*)?:\s*([^\n<]+)/
    )?.[1];
    return {
      title: `${name} · 활용 프롬프트`,
      summary: cleanPromptText(description ?? `${name} 스킬을 활용합니다`),
      when: `${name} 스킬이 필요한 작업을 요청할 때 사용하세요.`,
      body,
    };
  })
  .filter(Boolean);

const pages = pageDefinitions.map((page) => ({
  ...page,
  content: JSON.stringify(
    markdownToTiptapDoc(normalizeNotionMarkdown(page))
  ),
}));

if (
  pageDefinitions[0].raw.length < 15_000 ||
  pageDefinitions[1].raw.length < 1_000 ||
  prompts.length !== 41 ||
  !prompts.every((prompt) => prompt.body && prompt.summary && prompt.when)
) {
  throw new Error(
    `Page 또는 Prompt 구성이 불완전합니다. pages=${pageDefinitions.map((page) => page.raw.length).join(",")}, prompts=${prompts.length}`
  );
}

if (process.argv.includes("--check")) {
  console.log({
    pages: pageDefinitions.map((page) => ({
      title: page.title,
      chars: page.raw.length,
    })),
    skillCallouts: skillCallouts.length,
    prompts: prompts.length,
  });
  process.exit(0);
}

const db = new Database(resolve(root, "data/mymark.db"));
const findLocalPage = db.prepare(
  "SELECT id, content FROM custom_pages WHERE user_id = ? AND (title = ? OR content LIKE ?)"
);
const insertLocalPage = db.prepare(
  "INSERT INTO custom_pages (id, user_id, title, content, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"
);
const updateLocalPage = db.prepare(
  "UPDATE custom_pages SET title = ?, content = ?, updated_at = ? WHERE id = ? AND user_id = ?"
);
const localPageIds = {};
let localPages = 0;
let localPageUpdates = 0;
for (const page of pages) {
  const existing = findLocalPage.get(
    LOCAL_USER,
    page.title,
    `%${page.source}%`
  );
  const pageId = existing?.id ?? randomUUID();
  localPageIds[page.key] = pageId;
  if (!existing) {
    insertLocalPage.run(
      pageId,
      LOCAL_USER,
      page.title,
      page.content,
      now,
      now
    );
    localPages += 1;
  } else if (existing.content !== page.content) {
    updateLocalPage.run(page.title, page.content, now, pageId, LOCAL_USER);
    localPageUpdates += 1;
  }
}

const findLocalPrompt = db.prepare(
  "SELECT id FROM prompts WHERE user_id = ? AND title = ? AND category = ?"
);
const insertLocalPrompt = db.prepare(
  "INSERT INTO prompts (id, user_id, title, category, summary, when_to_use, sections, is_favorite, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (@id, @user_id, @title, @category, @summary, @when_to_use, @sections, 0, @created_at, @updated_at)"
);
let localPrompts = 0;
for (const prompt of prompts) {
  if (findLocalPrompt.get(LOCAL_USER, prompt.title, CATEGORY)) continue;
  insertLocalPrompt.run({
    id: randomUUID(),
    user_id: LOCAL_USER,
    title: prompt.title,
    category: CATEGORY,
    summary: prompt.summary,
    when_to_use: prompt.when,
    sections: JSON.stringify([
      { title: "프롬프트", body: prompt.body },
      {
        title: "관련 Page",
        body: `/pages/${localPageIds.departments}`,
      },
      { title: "원문", body: departmentPage.source },
    ]),
    created_at: now,
    updated_at: now,
  });
  localPrompts += 1;
}
db.close();

const sb = createClient(
  process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL,
  process.env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY,
  { auth: { persistSession: false } }
);
const prodPageIds = {};
let prodPages = 0;
let prodPageUpdates = 0;
for (const page of pages) {
  const { data, error } = await sb
    .from("custom_pages")
    .select("id, content")
    .eq("user_id", PROD_USER)
    .eq("title", page.title)
    .limit(1);
  if (error) throw error;

  const pageId = data?.[0]?.id ?? randomUUID();
  prodPageIds[page.key] = pageId;
  if (!data?.length) {
    const { error: insertError } = await sb.from("custom_pages").insert({
      id: pageId,
      user_id: PROD_USER,
      title: page.title,
      content: page.content,
      created_at: now,
      updated_at: now,
    });
    if (insertError) throw insertError;
    prodPages += 1;
  } else if (data[0].content !== page.content) {
    const { error: updateError } = await sb
      .from("custom_pages")
      .update({ title: page.title, content: page.content, updated_at: now })
      .eq("id", pageId)
      .eq("user_id", PROD_USER);
    if (updateError) throw updateError;
    prodPageUpdates += 1;
  }
}

let prodPrompts = 0;
for (const prompt of prompts) {
  const { data, error } = await sb
    .from("prompts")
    .select("id")
    .eq("user_id", PROD_USER)
    .eq("title", prompt.title)
    .eq("category", CATEGORY)
    .limit(1);
  if (error) throw error;
  if (data?.length) continue;

  const { error: insertError } = await sb.from("prompts").insert({
    id: randomUUID(),
    user_id: PROD_USER,
    title: prompt.title,
    category: CATEGORY,
    summary: prompt.summary,
    when_to_use: prompt.when,
    sections: JSON.stringify([
      { title: "프롬프트", body: prompt.body },
      {
        title: "관련 Page",
        body: `/pages/${prodPageIds.departments}`,
      },
      { title: "원문", body: departmentPage.source },
    ]),
    is_favorite: 0,
    created_at: now,
    updated_at: now,
  });
  if (insertError) throw insertError;
  prodPrompts += 1;
}

console.log({
  localPages,
  localPageUpdates,
  localPrompts,
  prodPages,
  prodPageUpdates,
  prodPrompts,
  localPagesByKey: Object.fromEntries(
    Object.entries(localPageIds).map(([key, id]) => [key, `/pages/${id}`])
  ),
  prodPagesByKey: Object.fromEntries(
    Object.entries(prodPageIds).map(([key, id]) => [key, `/pages/${id}`])
  ),
});
